1. *Plavi* oblaci se rasplinjavaju na nebu. (*Blue* clouds are dissipating in the sky.) 
2. Naše boje su *plave* i bele. (Our colors are *blue* and white.) 
3. Volim da nosim *plave* farmerke. (I like to wear *blue* jeans.)
4. *Plavim* svoju kosu već godinama. (I've been dyeing my hair *blue* for years.) 
5. Pogledaj *plave* oči te devojke. (Look at the *blue* eyes of that girl.) 
6. *Plavo* more izgleda prelepo na ovom kalendaru. (*Blue* sea looks beautiful on this calendar.) 
